 her own life with a gunshot to the breast. Probasco survived. The incident was widely reported nationally. The couple had no children.","body":"Roberta Ingersoll shot her companion Wallace Probasco then took her own life in her Park Avenue apartment, December 1926.","number":2,"category":"crime"}],"number_of_marriages":1,"cross_connections":[],"bio":{"display_name":"Robert Hawley Ingersoll","first_name":"Robert","middle_name":"Hawley","maiden_name":"Ingersoll","married_names":[]},"residence":{},"baptism":{},"research_tags":[],"research_sources":[],"documents":[],"naming_inspiration":[],"institutions":[],"landmarks":[],"artworks":[],"quotes":[],"military_service":[],"slug":"robert-ingersoll-1859"},"X00554":{"id":"X00554","has_descendants_documented":false,"classification":{"include_in_path_calculation":false,"descent_from_thomas_hooker":false,"descent_from_john_talcott":false,"is_thomas_descendant":false,"is_talcott_descendant":false,"is_easter_egg":false},"birth":{"year":1872},"death":{"year":1926,"cause":"suicide"},"tags":["suicide"],"sources":[],"marriages":[{"spouse_id":"HD1714","children_ids":[],"marriage_number":1,"date_year":1904,"date_month":6,"date_day":22,"location_city":"Muskegon","location_state":"Michigan"}],"gender":"female","number_of_marriages":1,"parents":{},"notable":{"is_notable":false,"notable_category":[]},"cross_connections":[],"bio":{"display_name":"Roberta Maria Bannister","first_name":"Roberta","middle_name":"Maria","maiden_name":"Bannister","married_names":[]},"residence":{},"baptism":{},"research_tags":[],"research_sources":[],"documents":[],"naming_inspiration":[],"institutions":[],"landmarks":[],"artworks":[],"quotes":[],"military_service":[],"slug":"roberta-bannister-1872"},"HD1715":{"id":"HD1715","has_descendants_documented":true,"classification":{"include_in_path_calculation":true,"generation_from_thomas":9,"descent_from_thomas_hooker":true,"descent_from_john_talcott":false,"is_thomas_descendant":true,"is_talcott_descendant":false,"is